(31, 1, '2009-08-07 12:07:58', '2009-08-07 10:07:58', '<span style="font-family: ''Trebuchet MS''; font-size: 13px;"> </span>\r\n<p align="justify"><strong>Les pages secrètes du blog du tueur fou de Bridgeville</strong>\r\n<span> </span><span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Etats-Unis<span> </span></strong></span>\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;">Article posté par<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="mailto:sbourgoin@au-troisieme-oeil.com">Stéphane Bourgoin</a><span> </span>le Jeudi 6 août 2009</span>\r\nLe tireur fou de Bridgeville,<span> </span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">George Sodini</span>, qui s''est suicidé après le massacre, tenait un blog qui a été retiré du Web.\r\n<span> </span>\r\nCe blog contenait des pages secrètes où il se confie. Nous avons pu en effectuer une capture avant sa disparition.\r\n<span> </span>\r\nL''homme tenait apparemment depuis novembre un "blog" dans lequel il laissait échapper sa haine des femmes. A la veille de la tuerie, il écrivait: "J''ai pris m...<span> </span>\r\n\r\n[<a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30717">lire la suite de l''article</a><span> </span>&gt;]\r\n<span> </span><strong>Actualité du Jeudi 6 août 2009</strong>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30722">Arizona: des garçons de 9 et 10 ans accusés de viol</a><span> </span>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30721">Iran: 24 personnes pendues en une journée</a><span> </span>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30720">Nancy : une jeune femme martyrisée avant d''être assassinée</a><span> </span>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30719">La police autrichienne tue un ado au cours d''un vol dans un magasin</a><span> </span>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30718">Un été de faits divers : Luc Tangorre, violeur ou bouc émissaire ?</a><span> </span>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30717">Les pages secrètes du blog du tueur fou de Bridgeville</a><span> </span>\r\n-<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.au-troisieme-oeil.com/index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr&amp;news=30716">L''auteur de la fusillade de Bridgeville l''avait annoncée sur son blog</a><span> </span>\r\n\r\n[<a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=accueil&amp;jour=2009-08-05">&lt; Jour précédent</a>] [<a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=actu&amp;type=skr#archives">Archives</a>] [<a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=accueil&amp;jour=2009-08-07">Jour suivant &gt;</a>]\r\n<table border="0" width="100%">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="40%" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">\r\n<span> </span><strong>Nouveaux livres de<span> </span><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=boutik">la librairie</a></strong>\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">André Héléna,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=272">Fanfan la douleur...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">André Héléna,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=271">Remise de peine...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">William Irish,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=270">Lady Fantôme...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Bernard Thomas,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=269">La bande à Bonnot...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Michel Meurger,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=268">Lovecraft et la S.-F / 1...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">S.T. Joshi,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=267">Clefs pour Lovecraft...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Didier Daeninckx &amp; Jean-Pierre Coureuil,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=266">Arcadius Cadin...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Eric Ambler,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=265">L''héritage Schirmer...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Cornell Woolrich,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=258">La mariée était en noir...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span> <span> </span><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Stéphane Bourgoin,\r\n<span> </span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=256">Le Cannibale de Milwaukee (1993)...</a><span> </span></span>\r\n</span></span></td>\r\n<td><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=book&amp;id=164"><img src="img/livre_164_200.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">\r\n<p align="right"><span> </span><strong><a style="color: #660c61; text-decoration: none;" href="index.php?page=calendrier">Le calendrier</a><span> </span>du 7 août 2009</strong></p>\r\n\r\nRien de prévu aujourd''hui !\r\n\r\n</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody></table>', 'page 4', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'page-4', '', '', '2009-08-07 12:16:03', '2009-08-07 10:16:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dev/1silex4wordpress/wordpress/?page_id=31', 0, 'page', '', 0);
</p>\n\n<div id="attachment_1093" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 310px;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="silex_wp" src="http://www.silexlabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/silex_wp-300x188.png" alt="silex_wp" width="300" height="188" />\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">Flash cms par Sha</p>\n\n</div>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">En janvier 2009, cest Sha qui sest chargée dorganiser les ateliers Silex.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">En mai 2009, Sha a été la pierre angulaire du<span> </span><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #eaab02;" href="http://www.silexlabs.com/a-propos/">Silex Lab</a><span> </span>: elle a concrétisé le travail de léquipe dev et de léquipe design en montant le nouvel outil Silex,<span> </span><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #eaab02;" title="Le manager, nouvel outil silex sorti avec la v1.5" href="http://hoyau.info/demos/silex_server/manager" target="_blank">The Manager</a>!</p>\n\n<div id="attachment_1097" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 310px;"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #eaab02;" href="http://hoyau.info/demos/silex_server/#manager-demo"><img style="border-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 5px;" title="manager de Silex v1.5 Comet" src="http://www.silexlabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/manager-300x170.jpg" alt="manager de Silex v1.5 Comet" width="300" height="170" /></a>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">manager de Silex v1.5 Comet</p>\n\n</div>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">Enfin, Sha est à la base de lhistoire damour entre un Silex et un<span> </span><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: #eaab02;" title="cd d''installation de l''imprimante badgy, développé avec Silex" href="http://hoyau.info/demos/cd-r_badgy/" target="_blank">CD dinstallation dimprimantes</a>!</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;">En 2009 elle ne sarrête plus de produire : des sites plus ou moins complexes, une dizaine de tutoriels, une trentaine de coups de pression et des tonnes dattentions.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Espérons que ça dure et que ça inspire, pour que peut-être un jour, lOpen Source prenne enfin ce côté féminin qui fait le charme de Silex.</strong></p>\n\n</span>', 'article 4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-autosave', '', '', '2009-08-07 12:19:04', '2009-08-07 10:19:04', '', 6, 'http://localhost/dev/1silex4wordpress/wordpress/?p=64', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
